description: Now monthly! Using his influence with government officials, Mr. Burns repeals the child labor laws in Springfield and finds he has a whole new workforce to exploit. Then, Grampa and Bart bond over a junky jalopy that they find at the police auction. Also, 'Maggie's Crib.'
name: Bart's Got Wheels; Maggie's Crib; The Nukes of Hazard

description: Now monthly! Bart, Milhouse, and Martin pull their resources together to buy a brand-new model kit that brings them together in more ways than one. Then, Principal Skinner and Bart enter into a war of words - sprayed on school property. In another tale, when Bart is assigned the task of interviewing a notable local resident, he chooses Hans Moleman. Also, 'Maggie's Crib.'
name: Model Behavior; The Invincible Principal; Maggie's Crib; Curse of the Moleman

description: Start of brief run of reprints of the Mind of Wolfie Smith from Tornado, under the French title Pat le Loup.

Tesla can’t free herself from the erotic dreams sent to her by Samael, Prince of the infernal Seductors: the beautiful vampire is really at risk of falling towards the Evil’s side. Trying to avoid this danger, Harlan Draka and Caleb Lost find out that Samael, for the help he gave them not so long ago, was kept under surveillance by Nergal, the dangerous chief of Hell’s secret police… To take Nergal off his back, Samael asks Harlan to recover a valuable artifact disappeared in the folds of the past: Dr John Dee’s mysterious “black mirror”, given to the alchemist by the self-appointed “Angel of the Western Window”, who actually was none other than the good devil, Nikolaus, in disguise. Allegedly, the mirror will endow its owner with a secure channel to the dangerous “Black Dimension”…
name: La casa di Faust

description: Rose Hill Prison is a ruthless world, where the inmates’ lives aren’t worth a lot… This time, though, it’s not the wardens’ violence to kill them, but a mysterious, peaceless ghost. The solution to this puzzling situation is a job for Dellroy Washington, the blind psychic. Behind the walls and the bars of Rose Hill, Dellroy and Harlan Draka will face human wickedness, along with an unknown horror, whose name is yet to be revealed…
name: Il penitenziario

description: For centuries, the invincible Be Helaket, the people “without death”, fought at the orders of Master of the Night Qeratu, the “Ghost”, unfailingly annihilating their enemies. And now they’re back. Taking advantage of the war situation in the Middle East, Qeratu created a profitable weapon-smuggling business at the border with Kurdistan. An exiled former-guerrilla, the legendary Commander Dal, wants to face the Master of the Night to avenge his comrades-in-arms, killed in a horrible bloodshed several years before. Dal is joined, of course, by the only effective vapire-slaying squad in the world, Harlan, Kurjak and Tesla’s. But entering in a war territory and reach the Master protected by vampire soldiers armed to the teeth won’t be easy…
name: I senza morte

description: Among Kurdistan’s deserts and plateaus, a no-holds-barred fight against the Be Helaket, the vampire soldiers led by the Master of the Night, Qeratu, rages on. Along with Dal, Wadid, Sirwa and their guerrillas, the vampire-buster quartet composed by Harlan, Kurjak, Tesla and Arno reaches the dead city of Habatja for the final clash. But not everyone will come out alive from the encounter with the Master…
name: Nel covo del Maestro

description: Who’s Zarema, the beautiful and sadistic owner of a private island in the Caspian Sea? Who are the hunters, the men that have a recurrent, long-standing appointment inside her property for a cruel man hunt? The only certain thing is the name of their prey: Harlan Draka! The Dampyr will have to fight for his life during a night of terror, to avoid that his head will be hung as a trophy inside the palace of the Mistress of the Darkness…
name: Stagione di caccia
Manifesto di Otto Krunz in regalo
Bravo Bellugi, ora non hai più niente da imparare!
Che succede al villaggio dei Puffi?
